         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Germanos, quintanensis, to Gaianos son of Himeros, greetings.  I have the quintana for Pauni, 16 (dr.), Pachon, 16 (dr.).  Year 12 of Nero the lord.</ab>
         </div>
